<div style="padding:30px 20px; color:#333;">
  <h2 style="margin-top:0; font-weight:600;">Action Required: Verify Your Email</h2>
  <p>Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
  <p>We received a request to reset the password for an American Surplus account associated with this email address.</p>
  <p>However, this account is not yet verified. Please verify your email first, then you can request a password reset again.</p>
  <p style="margin:20px 0;">
    <a href="<%= verifyUrl %>" style="background-color:#1976d2; color:#ffffff; padding:10px 16px; text-decoration:none; border-radius:4px; display:inline-block;">Verify Email</a>
  </p>
  <p>If you did not request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
  <p style="font-size:12px; color:#666;">For security, American Surplus does not reveal whether an email is associated with an account.</p>
</div>
